title: 2005 San Diego State Aztecs football team
text: The 2005 San Diego State Aztecs football team represented <a href="San%20Diego%20State%20University">San Diego State University</a> in the <a href="2005%20NCAA%20Division%20I-A%20football%20season">2005 NCAA Division I-A football season</a>. The Aztecs, led by head coach <a href="Tom%20Craft">Tom Craft</a>, played their home games at the <a href="Qualcomm%20Stadium">Qualcomm Stadium</a>.
